he most faults are the quickest of them to mention the faults of others.\u201d Source: al-S\u0323amt li Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 138 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064e\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8747,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/24\/ibn-sireen-entertainment-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":41873,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Sirin on Fun: Companions would have fun, sing poetry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurrah ibn Khalid reported: I asked Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cDid the companions have fun?\u201d Ibn Sirin said, \u201cThey were not but people. Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, would have fun and compose songs of poetry.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 2437 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31908,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/09\/ibn-sirin-beware-lowly-desires\/","url_meta":{"origin":41873,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Sirin on Whims: Do not listen to people of lowly desires",